<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5983">‌مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يَحْيَى </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3460">‌عَبْدُ الصَّمَدِ </a><span class="c2">(ح)</span>. وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/436">‌أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ الدَّارِمِيُّ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6555">‌النَّضْرُ </a>، جَمِيعًا عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةَ </a>بِهَذَا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ مُحَمَّدٌ:</span> لِلْعَقِبِ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ الْآخَرُ:</span> <span class="c2">«لِلْأَعْقَابِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>